Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲敲門有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：JoJo第2部中喬瑟夫的經典台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你還真是個過分的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  銳太同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你這是做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}認真的嗎  你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可愛的「女朋友」回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為只是去辦公室取個東西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說春咲同學不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了嗎  死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}哎呀  失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為面前的不是偷腥貓  而是偷腥的吉娃娃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰偷腥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不是還趁著女朋友不在的時候賴在銳太同學身上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是偷腥是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是這樣  是社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我交到男朋友以前的練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  我之前不是也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想變成萬人迷  就得先讀完全套JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們社團得不到學生會認可  沒有經費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就沒法集齊全套JoJo了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來  春咲同學當然只能找別人的男朋友偷腥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們社團被風紀委員盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也經常被罵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校的風紀委員權力很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是乎這就是今天的課題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(326.5,62)\frz1.3\fs22\t(0,600,\fs15.5)\1cA0868C\bord0}打倒風紀委員{\i1\fsp-10}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啦  不可能  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是要坐視社團被廢止咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加社團人數怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加兩個人就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好提議  春咲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你的頭蓋骨下竟然有大腦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你以為有什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆麵包的餡兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才吃的是咖哩麵包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重點在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  是哪個都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就來創作社團的主題歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22\bord0\1c765F60}來創作演出自我的少女會的「主題歌」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(318,52.5)\fs15\1c856A6F\bord0}來創作演出自我的少女會的「主題歌」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看了歌曲的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能結束戰爭  讓敵人改過自新
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能打倒終極Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的能量傳播能夠超越語言  國界和種族的阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果是電視劇或者動畫的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可能因為聽到某首歌而回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以歌曲會成為作品的門面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說如果借助主題歌來宣傳我社團的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生們就會嚷著「請讓我加入吧」蜂擁而至
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡  這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  我想到了一首好歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那春咲同學請講
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,題目是「和你的羈絆是汪汪喵」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE  LOVE  汪汪  汪汪喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶我說你  吶我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪了頭髮哦  有沒注意到？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有三公分  有沒注意到？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}那麼和你的距離  就是三公…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我全部聽完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒想過要更多地表現人類的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現孤獨靈魂的彷徨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這戀愛頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽這篇真正的詩歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後顫抖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(429,323)\fs20}世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,題目是「腐壞至極的這個時代」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}哇  等等等等  給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界  已然腐壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  就讓我來制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是小孩就輕視我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(397,323)\fs20}Beast
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街坊可是喚我為「暴走獸」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(407.5,323)\fs20}Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我將一切歸為虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}銳 認真聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我  我  我  我  Oh  零
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  快點注意到我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管時光怎麼流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你的羈絆都不會動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事嗎  銳太同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒有  沒有  什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貼得再緊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就看不出是男女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳太同學  你有什麼事瞞著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在社團活動室你也在偷瞄春咲同學的臉色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在我眼前對其他女生溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這獨佔欲是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不能告訴我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就在全校同學面前朗讀這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320.5,323)\fs20}Be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,323)\fs20}My
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(419,323)\fs20}Angel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守護我的四位美·舞·天使們」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那篇很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是也不能和別人討論情書的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管後果怎樣  這件事我不會說出口  絕不會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然對銳太同學來說  春咲同學很特別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  那邊那位就是小涼的男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺沒什麼魅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想看看小涼的男朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過其實你一點都不喜歡小涼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的  騙你的  開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個人要你來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說是讓我來看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然隔著電話  但是那邊聽上去很生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說送你回日本可不是為了讓你為所欲為的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像通過這邊議員之類的管道也瞭解了小涼在學校的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我會好好解釋的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能做讓小涼為難的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這傢伙會這麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小涼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為我幫你好好解釋的報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就讓給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠奪完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下次見面之前把各種事情都考慮清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是私立根中女子學院初中部三年級的夏川真那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我真那哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真涼的…妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次做比接吻更棒的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真涼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不要問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你不是在顫抖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有不想被觸及的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也一樣嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  你不游嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡被打濕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜  難得上一回游泳課
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還挺喜歡游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕飄飄地浮在水面上  盡情玩水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能像喬瑟夫和西撒那樣用波紋氣功在泳池水面上行走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺喜歡第1部和第2部的波紋戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那副樣子是想怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是故意遮遮掩掩擺架子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你不是說討厭被打濕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這不是溺水了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真涼  真涼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快振作起來  真涼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到嗎  真涼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我去把別的老師叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  山本  你在間接殺害你最喜歡的真涼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只能交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  全都這麼露骨地盯著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話先說在前面  接吻什麼的只是嘴和嘴貼在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群戀愛頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真涼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳太同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  你好點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我溺水了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是高中生了  真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵  溺水和初中高中沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  今天我對你的態度很奇怪  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  我也是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很討厭看到那孩子和銳太接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以為接吻什麼的只是嘴和嘴貼在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻覺得非常討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是因為我打探了你的秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和「男友」的初吻你明明還是用JoJo梗敷衍了事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個接吻的事你就不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也已經被覆蓋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆蓋  用什麼覆蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…就是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反…反正接吻和人工呼吸沒什麼區別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫真那的女孩的吻對於我來說就是「那又怎樣？」的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…總之別放在心上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會忘得乾乾淨淨的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把老師叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳太同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo第2部的波紋戰鬥  我也很喜歡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(142,77)\frz28\fs15\1c4B97C5\bord0}主題：不得了了，
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(174,130)\frz28\fs15\1c4B97C5\bord0}怎麼辦，吉娃娃{\1c4838B9\i1\fsp-8}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(308,292)\frz28\fs15\1c4B97C5\bord0}季堂同學和夏川真涼親親了{\1c4838B9\i1\fsp-8}！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發燒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  雖然不算嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是週六  我卻還有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  總是麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要的儘管說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫我擦一下身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要溫柔一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不是說了讓你溫柔點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興啊  銳好久沒來我的房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  有多久沒來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  銳  剩下的我自己來擦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那個時候的筷子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  我擅自拿來了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種東西要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是我最寶貴的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那個回憶  在我心裡永遠不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是銳交了女朋友也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上了別的女生也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的羈絆就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封情書不是千和寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們沒有必要重新締結羈絆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳  我也要人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  你不是有在呼吸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直都在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直陪著我吧  銳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去學人工呼吸也是為了千和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  千和  我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  銳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經徹底恢復了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  去上學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  真涼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  託你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  銳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹嘛一大早就秀恩愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是和青梅竹馬在一起的時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰秀恩愛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你在啊  偷腥吉娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早的就搶別人的男朋友  真是煩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰偷腥了啊  你說誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}當然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}這也是社團活動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像看到了什麼白色的紙片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你  我已經按捺不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放學後  在天台等你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(103,64)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,73)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0&}I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(103,128)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,139)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(103,192)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,204)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}U
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(103,256)\fs12\1cD9EBF3\bord0}法師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I  LOVE  U
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可說是「遙遠往昔的羈絆」有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是初次見面才對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我判斷銳太並未取回前世的全部記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在嘗試用這個世界的語言溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的咒文你讀懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指「I  LOVE  U」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在希伯來語中的意思是「羈絆  甦醒吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這個世界被叫做秋篠姬香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的名字是Himeka·靜·Heavensrain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(408,323)\fs20}Burning Prin Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我前世的名字則是「曉之聖龍公主」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(342.5,323)\fs20}Burning Fighting Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前世因強烈的羈絆與「曉之聖龍騎士」季堂銳太相互締結
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直好想見你  銳太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}啊  等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  秋篠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我希望你像以前一樣叫我「公主」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}註：日文中「姫（Hime）」同時有「公主」之義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(418.5,323)\fs20}Burning Fighting Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  公主  為什麼你會知道「曉之聖龍騎士」的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在前世曾與你有過誓約
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(265,323)\fs20}Wyvern
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要聯手同邪龍族戰鬥直到生命的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(233.5,323)\fs20}Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和偉大黑暗進行最終決戰的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問的不是設定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(418.5,323)\fs20}Burning Fighting Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟在哪裡聽說我是「曉之聖龍騎士」的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EKME點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EKME？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,323)\fs20}Ekimae
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個世界的語言來說就是「車站前」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是車站前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,323)\fs20}Wyvern
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(572.5,323)\fs20}Saint War
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是銳太同被邪龍族操縱的現世界人之間展開的那次聖戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳太釋放的氣場讓封印得以解開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於取回了前世的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是個現役「中二病」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銳  那女孩是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個花花公子呢  銳太同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集的可愛萬人迷道具是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備忘錄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做了什麼  眼神對上了  飯吃了那個  幾時睡的等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一舉一動都記錄下來  就能完成一部「男友物語」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專一的情思真是讓人心情激動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:40.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnArial}# 6{\r}  斬裂灰色世界的修羅場
